# Repository Defaults for TypeScript Projects

## CODEOWNERS

Must exist at: `.github/CODEOWNERS`

```
# All files require review from owner
* @${GITHUB_OWNER}
```

**Simple and complete** - All PRs automatically request review from repository owner

## Branch Protection (master)

Required settings in GitHub repository:
- ✅ Require pull request before merging
- ✅ Require approvals: 1
- ✅ Require review from Code Owners
- ✅ Require status checks to pass: build, test, lint
- ✅ Require branches to be up to date before merging
- ❌ Allow force pushes
- ❌ Allow deletions

## Project Board Columns

Standard workflow:
- **Backlog** - Issues not yet planned for current phase
- **Ready** - Issues defined in current phase, ready to work
- **In Progress** - Actively being worked on
- **In Review** - Pull request open, awaiting review
- **Done** - Completed and merged

## Repository Settings

- ✅ Issues enabled
- ✅ Projects enabled
- ✅ Automatically delete head branches after merge
- ✅ Allow squash merging
- ❌ Allow merge commits
- ❌ Allow rebase merging
